OL,3,CWoman, 93, fulfils dream of riding in
OL,4,Cpolice car
OL,6,FA 93-year-old woman has had a lifelong
OL,7,Fdream of travelling in a police car
OL,8,Fcome true.
OL,10,FFaith Whitaker from Helmshore in
OL,11,FRossendale, Lancashire, was given the
OL,12,Fopportunity by the Neighbourhood
OL,13,FPolicing Team to ride in the car, as
OL,14,Fan early Christmas wish.
OL,16,FThe grandmother, who is originally
OL,17,Ffrom the Lake District, moved to
OL,18,FRossendale more than 30 years ago and
OL,19,Fhas lived in Helmshore for the past 14
OL,20,Fyears.
