OL,3,CWoman, 93, fulfils dream of riding in
OL,4,Cpolice car
OL,6,FFaith was visited by PC Nigel Baxter,
OL,7,FPCSO Keely Dermody and PCSO Kirsty
OL,8,FBolton to fulfil one of her dreams of
OL,9,Fhaving a ride in a police car.
OL,11,FThe 93-year-old went out on patrol in
OL,12,Fher local area and kept her eye out
OL,13,Ffor anyone committing any crimes.
OL,15,FSatisfied with a job well done, Faith
OL,16,Fwas able to head home for a well-
OL,17,Fdeserved cup of tea. She said: "I've
OL,18,Fbeen looking forward to this, and I
OL,19,Fhad a great time being out and about
OL,20,Fwith the officers.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
