OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F397A1733577690
OL,3,CWoman, 93, fulfils dream of riding in
OL,4,Cpolice car
OL,6,F"It was brilliant, I didn't know what
OL,7,Fto expect but that was better than I
OL,8,Fhad hoped. Thank you so much to all of
OL,9,Fyou for making my day!"
OL,11,FHer desire to ride in a police car
OL,12,Fgrew from her love of watching police
OL,13,Fshows on television like Police
OL,14,FInterceptors.
OL,16,FPCSO Keely Dermody, who organised the
OL,17,Fvisit, said: "It was fantastic to meet
OL,18,FFaith and to hear all about her life.
OL,19,FWhen we were told that it was her
OL,20,Fdream to be taken out in a police car
OL,21,Fwe knew we wanted to make it happen.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
