OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F397A1733577690
OL,3,CWoman, 93, fulfils dream of riding in
OL,4,Cpolice car
OL,6,F"She was super excited to be able to
OL,7,Fget the opportunity, as she's always
OL,8,Fwanted to be a police officer, and her
OL,9,Fdaughter was thrilled we were able to
OL,10,Fgive Faith's the chance to live out
OL,11,Fher dream.
OL,13,F"As a team, we love being able to get
OL,14,Fout and meet the people in our
OL,15,Fcommunities.
OL,17,F"We want to show that we are more than
OL,18,Fa uniform, we're there to listen and
OL,19,Fto help, and we like to put smiles on
OL,20,Ffaces whenever we can."
